前工党政府[[英国外交大臣|外交大臣]][[杰克·斯特劳|杰克·斯特劳]]说，2010年首次当选的这一批议员可能是“30年来最好的”，他认为贾维德是“首个任期内就能有所表现”的六名保守党议员之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/columnists/article2665792.ece|title=These are the best new MPs for over 30 years|work=The Times|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015224902/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/columnists/article2665792.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>贾维德也是《[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]》着重分析的六名新的议员之一，并被保守主义网站评为2010年年度新人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/93221fb6-a638-11df-8767-00144feabdc0.html#axzz17QBm74qW|title=New MPs set out with confidence|work=Financial Times|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2013-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608062732/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/93221fb6-a638-11df-8767-00144feabdc0.html#axzz17QBm74qW|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://conservativehome.blogs.com/thetorydiary/2010/12/newcomer-of-2010.html|title=Newcomer of 2010|work=Conservative Home|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2011-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110209123224/http://conservativehome.blogs.com/thetorydiary/2010/12/newcomer-of-2010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年5月，威斯敏斯特的咨询公司Guide Public Affairs对2010年新当选的议员们进行分析后出版了《下一任首相指南》，贾维德得分位列第三，是保守党阵营的魁首。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guidepublicaffairs.co.uk/files/Guide%20To%20The%20Next%20PM%20Aug11.pdf |title=Guide Public Affairs |accessdate=2017-04-20 |archive-date=2012-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331121328/http://www.guidepublicaffairs.co.uk/files/Guide%20To%20The%20Next%20PM%20Aug11.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.bromsgrovestandard.co.uk/2011/08/25/story-Town-MP-tipped-to-be-future-PM-15721.html Story Town] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005164646/http://www.bromsgrovestandard.co.uk/2011/08/25/story-Town-MP-tipped-to-be-future-PM-15721.html |date=2011-10-05 }}</ref>2012年10月，《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的评论员{{le|伊恩·戴尔|Iain Dale}}将贾维德列入“右派百位最具影响力人物”榜单。<ref name="Dale1012"/>戴尔说：“贾维德如同涂抹了润滑油般的迅速升入[[乔治·奥斯本|乔治·奥斯本]]的核心圈子，这不仅是他的野心，更是他的天赋。”《[[卫报|卫报]]》的尼古拉斯·瓦特（Nicholas Watt）指出，贾维德可能会问鼎最高权力。<ref>Nicholas Watt [https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2013/jan/31/tory-party-rising-stars-fading "Tory party: the rising stars and those fading fast"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2013/jan/31/tory-party-rising-stars-fading |date=20170104014814 }}, theguardian.com, 31 January 2013</ref>

