4|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924054848/http://www.obv.org.uk/node/5327|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年9月4日，他正式加入奥斯本的[[英国财政部|财政部]]团队，任[[財政部經濟秘書|財政部經濟秘書]]。2013年10月7日改任[[財政部財務秘書|財政部財務秘書]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/ministerial-reshuffle-alistair-carmichael-replaces-michael-moore-as-scottish-secretary-8863953.html|title='Conspiracy theorist' Norman Baker replacement of Jeremy Browne heads list of reshuffle surprises|work=The Independent|accessdate=2015-01-28|location=London|first=Nigel|last=Morris|date=2013-10-07|archive-date=2013-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007182615/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/ministerial-reshuffle-alistair-carmichael-replaces-michael-moore-as-scottish-secretary-8863953.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

