=== 批评 ===
2014年3月1日，贾维德在下院指[[工党领袖_(英国)|工党领袖]][[爱德·米利班德|爱德·米利班德]]对[[克里米亚危机|克里米亚的危机]]负有责任，称米利班德拒绝支持[[2013年叙利亚化学武器袭击事件|对叙利亚的军事干预]]和随后俄罗斯在乌克兰的活动之间存在“直接联系”。其言论受到批评<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/10670566/Ukraine-tells-Putin-this-could-be-war.html|title=Ukraine tells Putin: this could be war|date=2014-03-01|work=Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2015-01-28|location=London|first=Damien|last=McElroy|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909055012/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/ukraine/10670566/Ukraine-tells-Putin-this-could-be-war.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2018年3月，贾维德在下议院中称左翼政治组织Momentum为“新法西斯主义者”。该组织回应称如果他在国会外重复{{le|国会特权|Parliamentary privilege}}的话将不能保护他免受起诉。下院议员[[约翰·曼|约翰·曼]]、[[乔恩·特里克特|乔恩·特里克特]]、{{le|克里斯·威廉姆森|Chris Williamson (politician)}}、{{le|亚历克斯·索贝尔|Alex Sobel}}、{{le|克莱武·刘易斯|Clive Lewis (politician)}}和[[卡罗琳·卢卡斯|卡罗琳·卢卡斯]]要求贾维德撤回声明并道歉。<ref name="independent">{{cite news|last=Kentish|first=Benjamin|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sajid-javid-momentum-neo-facist-labour-party-antisemitisim-jewish-a8280601.html|title=Sajid Javid threatened with legal action after calling Momentum 'neo-fascist'|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2018-03-29|accessdate=2018-04-02|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401004210/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sajid-javid-momentum-neo-facist-labour-party-antisemitisim-jewish-a8280601.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年7月，在工党领袖[[杰里米·科尔宾|杰里米·科尔宾]]威胁要将自己与[[犹太人大屠杀否定论|犹太人大屠杀否定论]]联系起来的言论采取法律行动后，贾维德回撤言论。工党议员指责贾维德“兜售谎言”，并呼吁[[特蕾莎·梅|特蕾莎·梅]]首相进行干预。<ref>{{cite news|last=Owen|first=Glen|date=2018-07-21|title=Sajid Javid backtracks after Jeremy Corbyn threatens legal action for linking him with Holocaust denial|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5978179/Sajid-Javid-backtracks-Corbyn-threatens-legal-action-linking-Holocaust-denial.html|newspaper=Mail on Sunday|accessdate=2018-07-22|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523125845/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5978179/Sajid-Javid-backtracks-Corbyn-threatens-legal-action-linking-Holocaust-denial.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Merrick|first=Rob|date=2018-05-21|title=Sajid javid backtracks on Jeremy Corbyn 'Holocaust denier' tweet following backlash|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sajid-javid-jeremy-corbyn-holocaust-denier-twitter-backlash-a8457706.html|newspaper=The Independent|accessdate=2018-07-22|archive-date=2018-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180721135333/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/sajid-javid-jeremy-corbyn-holocaust-denier-twitter-backlash-a8457706.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

贾维德拒绝了{{le|英国穆斯林理事会|Muslim Council of Britain}}关于保守党内有关仇视伊斯兰指控的{{le|独立调查|independent inquiry}}请求。<ref>{{cite news|last=Heffer|first=Greg|date=2018-06-03|title=Sajid Javid in Muslim Council of Britain spat over Islamophobia claims|url=https://news.sky.com/story/sajid-javid-in-muslim-council-of-britain-spat-over-islamophobia-claims-11393750|newspaper=Sky News|accessdate=2018-08-16|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817023422/https://news.sky.com/story/sajid-javid-in-muslim-council-of-britain-spat-over-islamophobia-claims-11393750|dead-url=no}}</ref>贾维德说：“英国的穆斯林理事会并不代表这个国家的穆斯林……我们不会与该理事会打交道。”理事秘书长Harun Khan声称：“令人遗憾的是，保守党有没有兴趣以应有的严肃处理这件事。”<ref>{{cite news|last=Zeffman|first=Henry|date=2018-06-04|title=Sajid Javid clashes with Muslim Council over Islamophobia|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/sajid-javid-clashes-with-muslim-council-over-islamophobia-63rfs5878|newspaper=The Times|accessdate=2018-08-16|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817001646/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/sajid-javid-clashes-with-muslim-council-over-islamophobia-63rfs5878|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 内阁大臣 ==

=== 文化大臣 ===
2014年4月9日，首相卡梅伦大规模改组内阁，提拔贾维德代替辞职的[[瑪利亞·米勒|玛丽亚·米勒]]担任{{le|文化传媒和体育大臣|Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport}}兼{{le|平权大臣|Minister for Women and Equalities}}。他再次成为2010年新人中的领跑者，和第一位领导[[英国政府部门|政府部门]]的[[巴基斯坦裔英國人|巴基斯坦裔]]议员。不久后，他又被任命为[[枢密院顾问官|枢密院顾问官]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sajid-javid|title=The Rt Hon Sajid Javid MP|work=www.gov.uk|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213141603/https://www.gov.uk/government/people/sajid-javid|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他成为文化大臣第一次做客BBC{{le|问题时间|Question Time (TV series)}}节目时表示自己会捍卫新闻自由和媒体调查政治家和官员的不法行为的权利。他说：“公众对于她如何回应的判断是正确的，绝对没有错。媒体...我不认为你可以责怪{{le|列文森委员会|Leveson Inquiry}}或媒体的某事。媒体是我们民主的基石，他们的自由是非常重要的，如果要调查政治家或其他公职人员的不法行为，他们应该这样做，没有什么可以阻止他们这样做。”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/apr/11/sajid-javid-maria-miller-bbc-question-time|title=Sajid Javid: media not to blame for Maria Miller's resignation|last=Mason|first=Rowena|work=The Guardian|date=2014-04-11|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2017-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618012716/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2014/apr/11/sajid-javid-maria-miller-bbc-question-time|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年5月有报道称，贾维德在3月份反对[[英国内政大臣|内政大臣]][[特蕾莎·梅|特蕾莎·梅]]提议给[[通讯管理局|通讯管理局]]以“反极端主义的权力”以便在广播前对英国电视节目进行审查的计划。他写信给首相[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]说，具有类似安排的国家“不知道这不符合与言论自由有关的权利，政府可能不希望与这种制度联系在一起”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/conservative/11622552/Theresa-Mays-proposal-to-censor-TV-was-opposed-by-cabinet-colleague-leaked-letter-reveals.html|title=Theresa May's proposal to censor TV was opposed by cabinet colleague, leaked letter reveals|last=Turner|first=Camilla|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2015-05-22|accessdate=2015-06-13|location=London|archive-date=2017-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421092044/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/conservative/11622552/Theresa-Mays-proposal-to-censor-TV-was-opposed-by-cabinet-colleague-leaked-letter-reveals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

作为文化大臣，他在2014年犹太学生联盟年会作的多样性的重要性和在文化世界中自由表达的演讲广受欢迎，《[[旁观者|旁观者报]]》的{{le|伊莎贝尔·哈德曼|Isabel Hardman}}评价为“我读过的最好的政府大臣演讲之一。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/coffeehouse/2014/12/is-this-the-best-speech-given-by-a-minister-in-this-government/|title=Is this the best speech given by a minister in this government?|last=Hardman|first=Isabel|work=Spectator Blog|date=2014-12-16|accessdate=2015-01-28|archive-date=2014-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226191927/http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/coffeehouse/2014/12/is-this-the-best-speech-given-by-a-minister-in-this-government/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 商务大臣 ===
[[2015年英国大选|2015年]]，保守党完全赢得大选，贾维德在[[卡梅伦第二政府内阁|新政府]]中担任{{le|商业创新及技能大臣|Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills}}。他当时被描述为“内阁最强劲的右派”，一个“真正的撒切尔主义者”。<ref>{{Cite news|title = Conservatives: the party of business?|url = http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/70295a84-c4f4-11e5-b3b1-7b2481276e45.html|newspaper = Financial Times|date = 2016-02-03|access-date = 2016-02-08|issn = |first = Jim|last = Pickard|archive-date = 2016-02-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204192302/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/70295a84-c4f4-11e5-b3b1-7b2481276e45.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>

贾维德被任命为商务大臣后表示，在保守党新政府领导下罢工的法律将会发生“重大变化”，影响基本公共服务的罢工将需要政府计划中符合资格的工会40％的成员的支持。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-32702585|title=Sajid Javid: Significant changes to strike law|accessdate=2015-05-12|work=BBC News|date=2015-05-12|archive-date=2017-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170526130958/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-32702585|dead-url=no}}</ref>

贾维德是英国留欧的支持者，尽管他把自己描述为“不想与欧洲更近一步”的欧洲人。<ref>{{cite news |last=Javid |first=Sajid |date=2016-05-14 |title=The only thing leaving the EU guarantees is a lost decade for British business |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/05/14/sajid-javid-the-only-thing-leaving-the-eu-guarantees-is-a-lost-d/ |newspaper=Daily Telegraph |location=London |access-date=2016-07-26 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918083345/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/05/14/sajid-javid-the-only-thing-leaving-the-eu-guarantees-is-a-lost-d/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年2月，法庭透露，贾维德不顾高级公务员的意见，不断向沙特阿拉伯颁发武器出口许可证，尽管沙特阿拉伯被指控领导[[沙特领导的干预也门行动|干预也门的行动]]是战争罪行。出口管制组织负责人爱德华·贝尔（Edward Bell）在2016年2月发出的的电子邮件是作为对英国对沙特阿拉伯销售武器的司法审查的一部分而被宣读的。电子邮件说：“说实话，我对[贾维德]非常直率和诚实，我的直觉告诉我，我们应该暂停[对沙特阿拉伯的武器出口]”。在后来的一封电子邮件中，他说：“[贾维德]决定不要在昨天晚上作出决定，现在已经与[首相]提出了这个问题。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/feb/07/official-advised-uk-minister-to-suspend-saudi-weapons-exports-court-hears |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-04-20 |archive-date=2017-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170208133601/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/feb/07/official-advised-uk-minister-to-suspend-saudi-weapons-exports-court-hears |dead-url=no }}</ref>

